CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.1
-------------------------

    o New function seqToGDS_ANNOVAR() for importing ANNOVAR-annotated VCF
      files (from table_annovar.pl -vcfinput) into SeqArray GDS format

    o new 'bsize' in seqAnnotate() and seqAnnotateGDS() to split the variants
      into blocks when 'add_to_gds' is TRUE or a file name: the annotation
      data are loaded and written block by block, so the memory usage no
      longer depends on the total number of variants (requiring the block
      writing in SeqArray::seqAddValue, SeqArray_v1.53.2)


CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.0
-------------------------

    o Initial Bioconductor package submission
